4712,"uid":325840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T08:00:47.000Z","msg":"原來可以咁樣幫還押手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1954173\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1954173</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"974c271992f307e57124f56fc5256d9e112ddcd5","tid":1954712,"uid":60644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T08:05:14.000Z","msg":"其實個電塔噉q大舊都可以撞埋去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，唔通係傳說中嘅天兵。定連戰機都偷工減料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89c2351a45f2b65b67b6f0eb80507451a9e5e37b","tid":1954712,"uid":47462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"974c271992f307e57124f56fc5256d9e112ddcd5","tid":1954712,"uid":60644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T08:05:14.000Z","msg":"其實個電塔噉q大舊都可以撞埋去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，唔通係傳說中嘅天兵。定連戰機都偷工減料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T10:49:02.000Z","msg":"個牌都係淘寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b68bc2e410e49089455e86d0ceab47a379a3a433","tid":1954712,"uid":186997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T10:56:34.000Z","msg":"平時演習唔係好威㗎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DVPC1UN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDVPC1UN.jpg&h=54f63c9c&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}